{"tid":207972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港唔可以推措施限制外國人買樓？","createTime":"2017-04-19T08:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T09:39:47.000Z","uid":94929,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8eac9edcbcd69d1f682a2655cba95881882e43","tid":207972,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"香港樓價雖然高到癲左，但經常睇到新聞話大陸客好豪咁一掃就幾層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳的新樓盤藍塘傲第一日揀樓既人竟然有4成係大陸人，個市完全資金推動，好難話會跌返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，點解香港唔可以限制外國人買樓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連上海都限制非上海居民最多只可以買一層，而且要係到做夠一年野同交足稅<br />\n而澳洲都有限制外國人買樓既措施(又係因為大陸人狂掃樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bc0b33e90a87a4c3a06ca926ff48a54a1054e9","tid":207972,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"港中融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ada744ee520fa916a7854ead626e1b15ba57602","tid":207972,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港中融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連上海都可以限制自己啲同胞既時候，唔明點解香港唔可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bec2d3d748f6c8815516ca1f21e1e6eae50a1fb","tid":207972,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"同埋淨係加稅對大陸班暴發户既阻嚇性根本唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且不停起新樓都消化唔切大陸班客，大陸有1%既人黎買樓都可以洩沒香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a29e89721a60a45634b2e81a5dd60247bc4f6d9","tid":207972,"uid":3876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"限蝗買樓-&gt;樓價跌<br />\n地產商一定唔制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府立例之前已經會俾建制ban左啦"},{"pid":"868a330265b9497628913d015fb52513794d9d08","tid":207972,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港中融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連上海都可以限制自己啲同胞既時候，唔明點解香港唔可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府幾時有從香港人嘅角度出發?"},{"pid":"17119b1e913252f9b161afa790a32cc54b3a0208","tid":207972,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>限蝗買樓-&gt;樓價跌<br />\n地產商一定唔制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府立例之前已經會俾建制ban左啦</blockquote><br />\n真心覺係得返衣條例係有可能壓抑到樓市，希望多啲人睇到一齊反映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連限奶令都有，點解唔可以有限樓令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到宜家山卡啦都成500萬就覺得好心寒"},{"pid":"d0d752d2fd5668e9cf3bb8a3f9996e8647d6d849","tid":207972,"uid":94929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>港中融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連上海都可以限制自己啲同胞既時候，唔明點解香港唔可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n政府幾時有從香港人嘅角度出發?</blockquote><br />\n連偉大既祖國都有，點解香港政府可以唔跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7b7703d4f5d850fbc6fc4a8ceb4018caed701b","tid":207972,"uid":45432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港樓價雖然高到癲左，但經常睇到新聞話大陸客好豪咁一掃就幾層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">將軍澳的新樓盤藍塘傲第一日揀樓既人竟然有4成係大陸人</span>，個市完全資金推動，好難